Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忽然收到这封来信　你此刻所感到的困扰我十分明了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你可能已知道　为兄我在中国大陆安稳地生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不道歉以及不得不说的话堆积如山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能够与你见上一面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也因故无法前往你处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故派遣手下前来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日午后三时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:25.01,INFO03,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,译注：Public Garden， 又名Pubilc Park。即曾挂过某臭名昭著的"华人与狗不得入内"的告示之处。\N始建于清同治七年（公元1868年），曾名外滩公园，俗称外摆渡公园，大桥公园。\N1945年改称春申公园，次年1月改名黄浦公园。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在公共花园的黄浦江岸边等你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　我到底是在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明连地址都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐　您要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去百货店　钢笔坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是少爷给的那支钢笔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi桑怎么啦　你牙疼么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　哦　我吃口香糖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没见过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　这个啊　我还头一次吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜哟　真灵光叻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等不甜了就要吐掉哦　不能吞下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　你吃下去啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔　不能吞的么　唔　吞下去了会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会便当么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会便当的么？！那么可爱的风兰要就此便当了么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止　葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…你这头鬼畜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不住对不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决不原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位于共同租界区内的南京路　是上海最负盛名的商业中心街区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有着先施、永安、新新这三家字号的百货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加不久后即将落成的第四家百货--大新百货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们将这四家百货统称为「Big Four」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(发生了什么 怎么了)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没听见什么声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是爆炸声那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在放爆竹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是事故什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(着火啦！)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(开始打仗了！快点逃吧！)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(快跑！)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗　小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话联系不是不允许的么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小时光景前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上海总领馆处收到了犯罪预告书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预告说在南京路的四大百货里置放了炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那刚才的爆炸声是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是建设中的大新百货遭到了爆炸袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与驻军军官讨论后决定派你们前往调查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的线索呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过特地写了预告书　也没有一次性将四家百货同时爆破…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且　最先遭到爆炸袭击的是建设中的大新百货
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可见其首要目的并非要造成直接伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是威胁呢　还是为了转移视线呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带枪来了没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　那个…因为枪很重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:06:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　什么　永安　现在你在永安？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了　终于联系上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了　集中一下意识\N我给你们传输被置放了炸弹的地方的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着　你怎么会知道炸弹的所在？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是安装炸弹的男子故意给我看了炸弹的置放场所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体情况回头再跟你们说明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了　我现在就给你们传输画面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着　画面对应什么地方都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手间那里大概是先施百货　地板上有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楼梯转角平台的画面　慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从窗口可以看见新新和大新
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是在先施百货的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新新会挡掉视野　理应看不见大新
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那即是说是永安　就是你们现在的所在之处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的　但是不知道具体是几楼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说只能逐一彻查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的钟楼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新新百货
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁乱混进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛往新新　我去先施
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了　我们也开始搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　葛好像也遭到攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管对方很快就不见了身影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说各个百货里都至少有一名敌人么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也千万当心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这层楼没有发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往楼下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等　有人　有动静
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你　是你告诉了我炸弹的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走　去你哥哥那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那边么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从少爷那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有打算隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我自己都不能确信那到底是不是哥哥的来信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:12:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那男人打算将小姐带走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他真的是少爷的手下的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棗中弹了？没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所幸只是手臂受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边也确实有谁在的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还没有清楚看见对方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你是跟父母走散了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过可不能吞下呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能先出去一次了么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听见吗　对方好像也是能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛说的　和他拥有一样的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不好　对方只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头痛　该说运气好还是运气糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来拆除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行　这个炸弹能拆除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拆除起爆装置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹上制造者的意识有所残留　离远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楼上有人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在楼顶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等　棗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受伤了　帮忙找这个孩子的父母吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁　有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵的时限呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去没完没了的　看来只能下狠手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个百货店的广告气球中装有粉末状的毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不跟我走的话我就引爆气球了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么　你们到底想要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:18:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是能老老实实地去与你哥哥见面　也不至于将你卷入此事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走吧　和我一起去你哥哥那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有拒绝的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应是为了寻找你哥哥才来了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会知道这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍许有些窥读他人心思的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说有人打算弄断电线的话我马上就会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么哥哥不亲自来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的哥哥有要务在身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要务？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事　雪菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我哥哥的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他在说谎　内心多少会有所动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他的内心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对葛说　我用能力来动掉开关　让他趁机…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的　你使用能力的时限已过　无法使用能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且　我们的想法也已经被他看穿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快　一起走吧　你难道还有什么可犹豫的么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还能够使用能力么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟会被此等小把戏所蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有一瞬迟疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将传入脑海的话语信以为真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够窥探他人内心的能力妨害了你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　我爸妈在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了　终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸？这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是口香糖么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不多见　谁给你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　高千穂勲麾下的团体里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然也有拥有相同能力的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:21:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此　他们才会知道我们的能力并找上门来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛　就是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知他们计划在上海做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也未必是在上海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不好是策划好故意做给我们看的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他们正蠢蠢欲动这一点当不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信上除了些私事没别的　还给雪菜也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过　她竟回绝了哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝不是理所当然的么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今的高千穂勲只不过是我们的敌人罢了
